translations: 无铅的；不包铅的；不插铅条的

sentences.sentence: All new cars take unleaded petrol.
sentences.translation: 所有的新汽车都加无铅汽油。

sentences.sentence: Unleaded petrol rose more than a penny a gallon.
sentences.translation: 无铅汽油每加仑涨了一个多便士。

sentences.sentence: All its V8 engines will run happily on unleaded.
sentences.translation: 所有其V8引擎将靠无铅汽油良好运转。
